title: The_#1_Hits_of_the_70's_Part_3
description:
This is part three of five of "The Number One Hits of the 70's."

I've also included the next installment of all the controversy surrounding this show, and how it REALLY came to be. There is a universal version in a notepad and the souvenir photo-album version for which you will need Microsoft word, the Word Web App, or Word Viewer.

Fire Command: Time To Fire - When you are sure no one else is listening but you.
